' ============================================================
' Title:     nasim — Git Component Diagram
' Boundary:  nasim core library — Git group
' Purpose:   Version control awareness: status, diff, commit
' Milestone: v1.0
' Version:   5.0.0
' Source:    docs/prompt/p1.md — corrective architecture review
' Review:    docs/audit/audit.2026.06.20.comprehensive.reference.audit.md
